Firefox OS 2.5 test day - Friday, 16th of October, 2015
 
Welcome to today's testday! We will be testing Firefox OS 2.5 in preperation for release next month!

No previous testing experience is required. Moderators will be available on the #fxosqa IRC channel to answer questions and provide guidance. 

Please add yourself to the bottom of the pad so that everyone can get the proper recognition and so we know how well it went!!!!

IRC
Join us here:
